Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.36,0:00:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sassy Saddles,\Ndon't you just love
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,my new Femme Mystique\NChic line of gowns?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sequins and sashes,\NRarity, they're exquisite!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where in Equestria did\Nyou find the inspiration?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.67,0:00:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh. I modeled them after The\NAdventures of Shadow Spade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.72,0:00:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Her stories are always full\Nof mystery and suspense.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And best of all?\NFabulous costumes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.97,0:00:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They're perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.02,0:00:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, just making\Nsome minor adjustments.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.03,0:00:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadow Spade believes\Nit all comes down
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.32,0:00:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to attention to\Ndetail. And so do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.21,0:00:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There! Now it's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.68,0:00:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey guys! How's it--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.39,0:00:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh heh. My bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.35,0:01:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hearing impaired subtitles\Nby YayPonies\NWe have muffins!\Nhttp://yayponies.eu/
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.87,0:01:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I messed up\Nyour dress thingie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.44,0:01:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing we can't\Nfix in a stitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing\Nin Canterlot?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.74,0:01:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here for Princess Celestia's\NRoyal Garden Opening tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.01,0:01:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.32,0:01:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumor has it the gardens are\Nespecially lush this season.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:01:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that the Wonderbolts\Nwill be kicking things off
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.43,0:01:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,with an aerial display.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.69,0:01:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And Rainbow Dash is\Nhere to fly with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.18,0:02:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.49,0:02:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, kind of exciting.\NTechnically I'm not flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.55,0:02:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just the lucky\Nreserve who was called in
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.41,0:02:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,to be the back-up flier in case\Na Wonderbolt can't perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't be so modest!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.46,0:02:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of all the reserves,\Nyou were the one chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It is pretty sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.47,0:02:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I do get to\Nstay in the castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,hang out with\Nthe Wonderbolts,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.51,0:02:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and eat awesome food\Nat the dinner tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.07,0:02:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of the dinner,\Nyou're still coming right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Heavens yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A chance to dress up, be\Ncharming and show off
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,my newest femme\Nmystique couture?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't miss it\Nfor all of Equestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. See you tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, the rhinestones\NI ordered!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my, oh, there's\Nbeen a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.26,0:02:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I ordered dragon cut stones\Nand these are hoof-polished.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.14,0:03:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I've got a full\Nload of deliveries today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure I have\Ntime to redo your order.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you don't!\NYour job is so difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I don't know how you\Nkeep all those orders straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It is pretty tough, what with\Nthe boxes all being box-shaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, and I very\Nmuch appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But if there was any\Nway you could squeeze in
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,one more little delivery, I\Nwould be eternally grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha. Well, for you,\NRarity, I'll see what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, you could sweet\Ntalk a filly out of candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was nothing. No\Npony minds a compliment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you simply must help me\Npick out an outfit for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.38,0:03:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Something from the new\Ncollection, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's grab some grub!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmmmm. Is that\NJuniper Phoenix I smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.64,0:04:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's broccoli!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, Juniper Phoenix is one of{\i0}\N{\i1} my favorite stallion colognes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine as well. It's\Nmasculine, and yet soft,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,with the barest hint of\Nfloral notes and a --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, don't you\Nknow who this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A gentlepony with fabulous\Ntaste in colognes and scarves?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Wind Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! So nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't let me finish!\NHe's a living legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.23,0:04:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He holds the Wonderbolt record\Nin the Mustang Marathon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that was a\Nlong time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I can't believe\NI still hold the record.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wind Rider, I see\Nyou met Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She's one of our most\Npromising reserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She just might\Nbeat your record!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Really now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm nowhere\Nnear as good as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean I'm fast, but I\Ndon't have the endurance
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to go long distances.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.43,0:05:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be modest.\NA little practice
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll be beating\Nrecords in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.98,0:05:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh. Well, it's nice\Nto meet you fillies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not as nice as\Nit is to meet you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I\Njust met Wind Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He's coming\Nout of retirement
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to take the spot of honor\Nin the center of our
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,aerial flower\Nformation tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll just watch\NWind Rider being awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,from the sidelines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Practice tomorrow is\Ngonna be so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose I\Ncould keep you company?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:05:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You could!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.01,0:06:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They always let friends and\Nfamily come watch practices.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that. Let\Nme help clean that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No no. It's almost impossible\Nto get stains out of silk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But not to worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That dinner was absolutely\Ndivine! Thanks for inviting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.89,0:06:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! You're staying\Nin the east tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Those rooms have the\Nbest view of Canterlot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How lucky are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we better get some\Nshuteye before practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow, Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for keeping\Nme company, Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.69,0:06:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you weren't here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,well, I don't know who I'd\Nbe talking to right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:06:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd be talking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.62,0:07:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, Spitfire's\Nmom sent a message
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that she was sick. She had to\Nleave to take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! I hope her mom's OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too. In the meantime, we\Nneed you to fly in her place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,L-l-like in the actual show?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless Spitfire comes back, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you down, Soarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.28,0:07:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,AAAAH! This is the\Nbest thing EVERRR!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh oh my gosh\Noh my gosh oh my gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ I'm gonna get to fly with Wind{\i0}\N{\i1} Rider! And the Wonderbolts! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Cause I'm the bestest! And I'm{\i0}\N{\i1} awesome! And they know it! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhhh. Rainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.02,0:07:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh sh. Let her\Nhave this, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, there. Friend or family?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Family. My daughter's\Na Wonderbolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:08:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't see her up\Nthere. Do you know Spitfire?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're Spitfire's mom?\NBut I thought you were sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Spitfire got\Na note from you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,saying you weren't\Nfeeling well
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.74,0:08:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and she went home\Nto take care of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't send a note.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.75,0:08:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Stormy Flare? Aren't you\Nsupposed to be sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.46,0:08:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but I do know I\Ndidn't send my daughter a note.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Could somepony have sent\NSpitfire a fake note?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Somepony who wanted her\Nout of the show, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would anypony want that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe so that they\Ncould take her spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? I would never\Ndo that to Spitfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you think it was me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I did see you and Spitfire\Nleave the dinner together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We were room neighbors\Nin the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And you did say you would do\Nanything to fly with Wind Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:09:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I didn't\Nmean anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.96,0:09:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Spitfire came by my room
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and told me she had to go see\Nher mom at around midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.84,0:09:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was asleep at midnight, having\Nthis totally amazing dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There I was at the arena,\Nflying with Wind Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Wonderbolts, like\NI've always wanted to--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind. Not helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.49,0:09:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, if you can prove\Nthat somepony else is behind
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Spitfire's disappearance\Nbefore the start of the show,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,then you can still fly with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime,\NMisty Fly, Blaze,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,head over to Stormy Flare's\Nhouse and try to find Spitfire
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and bring her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to warn you, if\Nyou sent that letter,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the bylaws are clear;\NI'd have no choice
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but to ban you from the\NWonderbolts forever. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. But how am I gonna\Nprove I didn't send a letter
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:09:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that I didn't send?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,With me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.09,0:10:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective Rarity is on the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're going to get\Nto the bottom of this
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,faster than my\Ncostume change!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what's\Nwith the get-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.68,0:10:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, I am\Nchanneling Shadow Spade
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,through these\Ngorgeous garments.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And she would say that\Nthe best way to prove
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.98,0:10:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that you didn't send the letter\Nis to find out whoever did!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,First stop, the\Nscene of the crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We had a long road ahead{\i0}\N{\i1} of us, Rainbow Dash and I.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Well, not too long because{\i0}\N{\i1} we didn't have much time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} but the point is, I was{\i0}\N{\i1} up for the challenge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.48,0:10:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There I was, surveying\Nthe crime scene
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and looking tres\Nchic while doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be the envelope\Nfor the letter Spitfire got!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:11:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, these look like\Nhairs from a rainbow mane!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rainbow Dash was getting antsy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} But I had faith I{\i0}\N{\i1} could clear her name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} and find the real culprit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, oh what? Oh,\Njust thinking thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Rainbow Dash was right. In{\i0}\N{\i1} order to solve the mystery,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} we had to be focused, driven,{\i0}\N{\i1} one hundred percent in the--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The damask pattern on these\Ncurtains is exquisite!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.26,0:11:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and this velvet\Nrope holder, oh it's--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time\Nto look at the decor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gonna kick me\Nout of the Wonderbolts
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,unless we solve this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, Rainbow, and\NI am on this case
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,like a charm on a bracelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's what I'm thinking:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.53,0:11:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,somepony had to bring\NSpitfire that letter,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,which means somepony\Nmust have seen them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:11:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have a few\Nquestions for you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:12:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm sure once we get some\Nthings cleared up, we'll--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Rarity; we\Ndon't have all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you on the night\Nof last night at midnight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We were here, guarding\Nthe hallway entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,like we were supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.82,0:12:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A likely story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.63,0:12:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, we\Nwere there all night
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and no one went in or\Nout of that hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Except for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just that there are only two\Nrooms in the northwest wing:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,yours and Spitfire's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.50,0:12:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So the only other pony who had\Naccess to that wing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The waters were getting choppy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Rainbow Dash's tactics{\i0}\N{\i1} were... well, horrid.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} It was time for{\i0}\N{\i1} another approach.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I should\Ntake it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.08,0:12:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You castle guards have\Nsuch a difficult job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing that at times,\Nit can be rather boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It is. I've counted all\N345 bolts in the ceiling tiles
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,293 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.81,0:13:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, being a castle\Nguard can be thankless work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying you did,\Nbut if you took a break,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you more than deserved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, you're right, we don't\Nget a lot of recognition
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,for what we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Except for last night when\Nsomepony was nice enough
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to leave a cake for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So we did take one little\Nbreak when we ate that cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of cake was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Cherry with a\Ncustard filling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the frosting\Nvanilla or chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it decorated with\Nbuttercream rosettes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It was!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. Who cares how\Nit was decorated?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Rainbow Dash was{\i0}\N{\i1} questioning my methods,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} but I knew what I was doing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Did I say that\None out loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, even I think I'm\Nguilty at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.33,0:13:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I really did want\Nto fly in that show!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I wrote that\Nnote when I was asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.06,0:13:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what I do when I\Nsleep? Because I sure don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, calm down, Rainbow Dash.\NWe'll get to the bottom of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.09,0:13:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one\Nbakery in Canterlot
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that makes a chocolate cherry\Ncake with custard filling
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:13:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and buttercream frosting\Nrosettes, and that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...Cinnamon Chai's\NTea and Cake Shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.58,0:14:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, how can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard you have the best\Nchocolate cherry custard cake
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.51,0:14:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,with buttercream frosting\Nrosettes in town!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.88,0:14:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! You travel in\Nthe right circles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We have the only chocolate\Ncherry custard cake
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.03,0:14:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,with buttercream frosting\Nrosettes in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.70,0:14:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! But somepony's\Nalready bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was the lucky pony?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.39,0:14:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even say!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.23,0:14:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because it was\Nsomepony famous?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Because it\Nwas hard to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.27,0:14:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She was wearing a trenchcoat,\Nsunglasses, and a scarf
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.17,0:14:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,around her head that\Ncovered most of her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.97,0:14:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I do remember she had a\Nreally deep, raspy voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What do\Nyou mean raspy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, kinda like yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's anything else\Nyou can remember, dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.09,0:14:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, have I got\Na story for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The pony who bought the\Ncake threw a big fit
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.82,0:15:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,when she accidentally got\Nchocolate ganache on her scarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's terrible! What\Ncolor was the scarf?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,White. No, maybe\Nmore of an ivory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't say!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.67,0:15:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you're talking\Nfashion at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow, don't panic.\NI need you to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust you? You've spent\Nmore time changing clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,than trying to help\Nme. I'm doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're not. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rainbow Dash was obviously upset{\i0}\N{\i1}but I had all my ducks in a row,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} except for one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} She was not going to like it,{\i0}\N{\i1} but there was only one way{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} to find out if my{\i0}\N{\i1} suspicions were correct.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We looked everywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but Spitfire wasn't\Nat her mom's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.07,0:15:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could she be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.80,0:16:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've found the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.93,0:16:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Somepony sent Spitfire away and\Nframed Rainbow Dash for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And that pony was none\Nother than... WIND RIDER!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, I can't believe you\Nwould accuse Wind Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.18,0:16:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,of framing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.34,0:16:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a living legend,\Nfor pony's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All the evidence points to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What evidence could\Nyou possibly have?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All you did was ask\Nabout cake, admire decor,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and change outfits\Na gazillion times.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.77,0:16:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I never believed you\Nwould send Spitfire away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.74,0:16:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we found the rainbow\Nhairs in Spitfire's room,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.18,0:16:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I could tell they didn't\Nfall out; they were cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No pony loses hair in a chunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And look at the ends;\Nit's a straight line!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.48,0:16:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They were clearly\Ncut with shears!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means somepony planted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, when we were examining\NSpitfire's room...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...I smelled something on the\Nenvelope. Juniper Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wind Rider's cologne of choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, in the castle hallway,\NI noticed some of the damask
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.94,0:17:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,curtains fell out of\Ntheir velvet rope holder,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,indicating that somepony had\Nbeen hiding behind them,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.88,0:17:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,perhaps after they dropped\Noff the fake letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Juniper Phoenix is a\Nvery popular fragrance
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and anypony could have\Nmoved those curtains.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely why I questioned\Nthe castle guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.27,0:17:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They were at their post at\Nthe entrance to the hallway
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,all night except for\Na small window of time
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.63,0:17:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,when somepony brought them cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A cake that was ordered by a\Ngirl pony with a raspy voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever ordered the cake\Ngot a chocolate stain
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.34,0:17:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,on their ivory scarf, and\NI couldn't help but notice
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wind Rider's scarf is tied\Nin a tight Windsor knot
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of its usual\Nloose slipknot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:18:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And why is that? Is it to\Nhide... the chocolate stain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is preposterous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderbolts, you don't\Nbelieve a word of this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.39,0:18:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just admit it! You're as\Nguilty of framing Rainbow Dash
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,as you are of ruining\Nthat ivory scarf!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. You caught me! I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But why, Wind Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.14,0:18:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because I took\Nthe last broccoli
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,at the dinner and you\Nreally really wanted it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It was because he was afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that you would break his long\Ndistance Wonderbolt record.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard him when Spitfire said
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you were close to\Nbreaking his record.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He said and I quote, "heh heh."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.12,0:18:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the polite but\Ndisingenuous laugh you make
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,when you want to seem happy\Nbut really you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought if I could\Nget Rainbow Dash
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.87,0:18:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,kicked out of the\NWonderbolts forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.95,0:18:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,my record would be preserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.34,0:18:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That is so not cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were the coolest\NWonderbolt ever until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:18:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I did what I had to do\Nto protect my record.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, you gotta play\Ndirty to be the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.59,0:19:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what being a\NWonderbolt is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.09,0:19:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderbolts look\Nout for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Which reminds me,\Nwhere is Spitfire?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I sent her the letter\Npretending to be Stormy Flare.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I told her I had Pegasitus\Nand the only cure
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is the Ice Iris in\Nthe Crystal Mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder she's\Nbeen gone so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice Irises are almost\Nimpossible to find in spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The Crystal Mountains are too\Nfar for anypony to make it there
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and back before the\NRoyal Garden opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, we need you\Nto fly in Spitfire's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But Spitfire shouldn't have to\Nmiss this. I'm gonna get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you'll never\Nmake it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's no time to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash is still gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.74,0:19:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If I know Rainbow Dash,\Nshe'll come through.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:20:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Spitfire, you're back! I\Ncan't believe you made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.78,0:20:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I wouldn't have, if Rainbow\Nhadn't found me so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.69,0:20:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Gave me enough time to fly back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Rare, I couldn't have\Ndone it without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm sorry\NI doubted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But why didn't you tell\Nme what you were doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't want to get your\Nhopes up until I was sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And I couldn't be sure until\NI saw that chocolate stain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for believing in me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...even when I was doubting\Nyou. I'm some friend, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, you're\Nquite a good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You went to get Spitfire,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,even though it meant\Nyou couldn't fly today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.57,0:20:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get\Nmy chance one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Or today. How'd you like Wind\NRider's spot in the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You can't\Ndo this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.68,0:20:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm one of the greatest\NWonderbolts there ever was!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Not anymore. For attempting\Nto frame Rainbow Dash,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I hereby strip you of\Nyour Wonderbolt status!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So would you like\Nto fly with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:21:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Would I? Woo-hoo!\NYeah-yeah-yeah-yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh, Uh-huh!\NYeah! Oh, YEAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.33,0:21:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Rainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.14,0:21:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So my friend got{\i0}\N{\i1} her moment in the sun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.71,0:21:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Or the center of an aerial{\i0}\N{\i1} flower as the case may be.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.28,0:21:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} And as for me? I got a{\i0}\N{\i1} chance to show off my{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Femme Mystique Chic collection!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.00,0:21:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nice, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Did I say\Nthat out loud?
